ryHTML":"<h3>Books</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://arxiv.org/pdf/1404.7828v4.pdf\">Deep Learning in Neural Networks: An Overview</a></li>","updatedAt":"2015-08-05T13:11:57.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"ChristosChristofidis/awesome-deep-learning","categoryHTML":"<h2>Researchers</h2><h3>Datasets</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://www.science.uva.nl/~aloi/\">Amsterdam Library of Object Images</a> - ALOI is a color image collection of one-thousand small objects, recorded for scientific purposes. In order to capture the sensory variation in object recordings, we systematically varied viewing angle, illumination angle, and illumination color for each object, and additionally captured wide-baseline stereo images. We recorded over a hundred images of each object, yielding a total of 110,250 images for the collection. (Formats: png)</li>","updatedAt":"2015-08-05T13:11:57.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"ChristosChristofidis/awesome-deep-learning","categoryHTML":"<h2>Researchers</h2><h3>Datasets</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://www.uk.research.att.com/facedatabase.html\">AT&#x26;T Laboratories Cambridge face database</a></li>","updatedAt":"2015-08-05T13:07:49.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"ChristosChristofidis/awesome-deep-learning","categoryHTML":"<h2>Researchers</h2><h3>Datasets</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://xtreme.gsfc.nasa.gov\">AVHRR Pathfinder</a></li>","updatedAt":"2015-08-05T13:07:49.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"ChristosChristofidis/awesome-deep-learning","categoryHTML":"<h2>Researchers</h2><h3>Datasets</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://www.anc.ed.ac.uk/~amos/afreightdata.html\">Air Freight</a> - The Air Freight data set is a ray-traced image sequence along with ground truth segmentation based on textural characteristics. (455 images + GT, each 160x120 pixels). (Formats: PNG)</li>","updatedAt":"2015-08-05T13:07:49.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"ChristosChristofidis/awesome-deep-learning","categoryHTML":"<h2>Researchers</h2><h3>Datasets</h3>","itemHTML":"<l