Researchers</h2><h3>Datasets</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://github.com/ChristosChristofidis/awesome-deep-learning/blob/master/cil-ster.html\">CMU CIL's Stereo Data with Ground Truth</a> - 3 sets of 11 images, including color tiff images with spectroradiometry (Formats: gif, tiff)</li>","updatedAt":"2015-08-05T13:07:49.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"ChristosChristofidis/awesome-deep-learning","categoryHTML":"<h2>Researchers</h2><h3>Datasets</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://www.ri.cmu.edu/projects/project_418.html\">CMU PIE Database</a> - A database of 41,368 face images of 68 people captured under 13 poses, 43 illuminations conditions, and with 4 different expressions.</li>","updatedAt":"2015-08-05T13:07:49.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"ChristosChristofidis/awesome-deep-learning","categoryHTML":"<h2>Researchers</h2><h3>Datasets</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://www.ius.cs.cmu.edu/idb/\">CMU VASC Image Database</a> - Images, sequences, stereo pairs (thousands of images) (Formats: Sun Rasterimage)</li>","updatedAt":"2015-08-05T13:07:49.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"ChristosChristofidis/awesome-deep-learning","categoryHTML":"<h2>Researchers</h2><h3>Datasets</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://www.vision.caltech.edu/html-files/archive.html\">Caltech Image Database</a> - about 20 images - mostly top-down views of small objects and toys. (Formats: GIF)</li>","updatedAt":"2015-08-05T13:07:49.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"ChristosChristofidis/awesome-deep-learning","categoryHTML":"<h2>Researchers</h2><h3>Datasets</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://www.cs.columbia.edu/CAVE/curet/\">Columbia-Utrecht Reflectance and Texture Database</a> - Texture and reflectance measurements for over 60 samples of 3D texture, observed with over 200 different combinations of viewing and illumination directions. (Formats: bmp)</li>","updatedAt":"2015-08-05T13:07:49.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"ChristosChristofidis/awesome-deep-learning","categoryHTML":"<h2>Researchers</h2><h3>Datasets</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://www.cs.sfu.ca/~colour/data/index.html\">Computational Colour Constancy Data</a> - A dataset oriented towards computational color constancy, but useful for computer vision in general. It includes synthetic data, camera sensor data, and over 700 images. (Formats: tiff)</li>","updatedAt":"2015-08-05T13:07:49.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"ChristosChristofidis/awesome-deep-learning","categoryHTML":"<h2>Researchers</h2><h3>Datasets</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://www.cs.sfu.ca/~colour/\">Computational Vision Lab</a></li>","updatedAt":"2015-08-05T13:07:49.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"ChristosChristofidis/awesome-deep-learning","categoryHTML":"<h2>Researchers</h2><h3>Datasets</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://www.cs.washington.edu/research/imagedatabase/\">Efficient Content-based Retrieval Group</a></li>","updatedAt":"2015-08-05T13:07:49.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"ChristosChristofidis/awesome-deep-learning","categoryHTML":"<h2>Researchers</h2><h3>Datasets</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://ls7-www.cs.uni-dortmund.de/~peters/pages/research/modeladaptsys/modeladaptsys_vba_rov.html\">Densely Sampled View Spheres</a> - Densely sampled view spheres - upper half of the view sphere of two toy objects with 2500 images each. (Formats: tiff)</li>","updatedAt":"2015-08-05T13:07:49.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"ChristosChristofidis/awesome-deep-learning","categoryHTML":"<h2>Researchers</h2><h3>Datasets</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://ls7-www.cs.uni-dortmund.de/\">Computer Science VII (Graphical Systems)</a></li>","updatedAt":"2015-08-05T13:07:49.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"ChristosChristofidis/awesome-deep-learning","categoryHTML":"<h2>Researchers</h2><h3>Datasets</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://www.gastrointestinalatlas.com\">El Salvador Atlas of Gastrointestinal VideoEndoscopy</a> - Images and Videos of his-res of studies taken from Gastrointestinal Video endoscopy. (Formats: jpg, mpg, gif)</li>","updatedAt":"2015-08-05T13:07:49.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"ChristosChristofidis/awesome-deep-learning","categoryHTML":"<h2>Researchers</h2><h3>Datasets</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://sting.cycollege.ac.cy/~alanitis/fgnetaging/index.htm\">FG-NET Facial Aging Database</a> - Database contains 1002 face images showing subjects at different ages. (Formats: jpg)</li>","updatedAt":"2015-08-05T13:07:49.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"ChristosChristofidis/awesome-deep-learning","categoryHTML":"<h2>Researchers</h2><h3>Datasets</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://bias.csr.unibo.it/fvc2000/\">FVC2000 Fingerprint Databases</a> - FVC2000 is the First International Competition for Fingerprint Verification Algorithms. Four fingerprint databases constitute the FVC2000 benchmark (3520 fingerprints in all).</li>","updatedAt":"2015-08-05T13:07:49.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"ChristosChristofidis/awesome-deep-learning","categoryHTML":"<h2>Researchers</h2><h3>Datasets</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://www.fg-net.org\">Face and Gesture images and image sequences</a> - Several image datasets of faces and gestures that are ground truth annotated for benchmarking</li>","updatedAt":"2015-08-05T13:07:49.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"ChristosChristofidis/awesome-deep-learning","categoryHTML":"<h2>Researchers</h2><h3>Datasets</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://www-i6.informatik.rwth-aachen.de/~dreuw/database.html\">German Fingerspelling Database</a> - The database contains 35 gestures and consists of 1400 image sequences that contain gestures of 20 different persons recorded under non-uniform daylight lighting conditions. (Formats: mpg,jpg)</li>","updatedAt":"2015-08-05T13:07:49.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"ChristosChristofidis/awesome-deep-learning","categoryHTML":"<h2>Researchers</h2><h3>Datasets</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://www-i6.informatik.rwth-aachen.de/\">Language Processing and Pattern Recognition</a></li>","updatedAt":"2015-08-05T13:07:49.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"ChristosChristofidis/awesome-deep-learning","categoryHTML":"<h2>Researchers</h2><h3>Datasets</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://hlab.phys.rug.nl/archive.html\">Groningen Natural Image Database</a> - 4000+ 1536x1024 (16 bit) calibrated outdoor images (Formats: homebrew)</li>","updatedAt":"2015-08-05T13:07:49.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"ChristosChristofidis/awesome-deep-learning","categoryHTML":"<h2>Researchers</h2><h3>Datasets</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://www.icg.tu-graz.ac.at\">Institute of Computer Graphics and Vision</a></li>","updatedAt":"2015-08-05T13:07:49.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"ChristosChristofidis/awesome-deep-learning","categoryHTML":"<h2>Researchers</h2><h3>Datasets</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://www.ien.it/is/vislib/\">IEN Image Library</a> - 1000+ images, mostly outdoor sequences (Formats: raw, ppm)</li>","updatedAt":"2015-08-05T13:07:49.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"ChristosChristofidis/awesome-deep-learning","categoryHTML":"<h2>Researchers</h2><h3>Datasets</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://www-rocq.inria.fr/~tarel/syntim/images.html\">INRIA's Syntim images database</a> - 15 color image of simple objects (Formats: gif)</li>","updatedAt":"2015-08-05T13:07:49.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"ChristosChristofidis/awesome-deep-learning","categoryHTML":"<h2>Researchers</h2><h3>Datasets</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://www.inria.fr/\">INRIA</a></li>","updatedAt":"2015-08-05T13:07:49.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"ChristosChristofidis/awesome-deep-learning","categoryHTML":"<h2>Researchers</h2><h3>Datasets</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://www.ece.ncsu.edu/imaging/Archives/ImageDataBase/index.html\">Image Analysis Laboratory</a> - Images obtained from a variety of imaging modalities -- raw CFA images, range images and a host of \"medical images\". (Formats: homebrew)</li>","updatedAt":"2015-08-05T13:07:49.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"ChristosChristofidis/awesome-deep-learning","categoryHTML":"<h2>Researchers</h2><h3>Datasets</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://w