arning","categoryHTML":"<h2>Researchers</h2><h3>Datasets</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://www.middlebury.edu/stereo\">Middlebury Stereo Vision Research Page</a> - Middlebury College</li>","updatedAt":"2015-08-05T13:07:49.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"ChristosChristofidis/awesome-deep-learning","categoryHTML":"<h2>Researchers</h2><h3>Datasets</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://ltpwww.gsfc.nasa.gov/MODIS/MAS/\">Modis Airborne simulator, Gallery and data set</a> - High Altitude Imagery from around the world for environmental modeling in support of NASA EOS program (Formats: JPG and HDF)</li>","updatedAt":"2015-08-05T13:07:49.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"ChristosChristofidis/awesome-deep-learning","categoryHTML":"<h2>Researchers</h2><h3>Datasets</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"ftp://sequoyah.ncsl.nist.gov/pub/databases/data\">NIST Fingerprint and handwriting</a> - datasets - thousands of images (Formats: unknown)</li>","updatedAt":"2015-08-05T13:07:49.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"ChristosChristofidis/awesome-deep-learning","categoryHTML":"<h2>Researchers</h2><h3>Datasets</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://www.nlm.nih.gov/research/visible/visible_human.html\">NLM HyperDoc Visible Human Project</a> - Color, CAT and MRI image samples - over 30 images (Formats: jpeg)</li>","updatedAt":"2015-08-05T13:07:49.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"ChristosChristofidis/awesome-deep-learning","categoryHTML":"<h2>Researchers</h2><h3>Datasets</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://eewww.eng.ohio-state.edu/~flynn/3DDB/Models/\">OSU (MSU) 3D Object Model Database</a> - several sets of 3D object models collected over several years to use in object recognition research (Formats: homebrew, vrml)</li>","updatedAt":"2015-08-05T13:07:49.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"ChristosChristofidis/awesome-deep-learning","categoryHTML":"<h2>Researchers</h2><h3>Datasets</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://eewww.eng.ohio-state.edu/~flynn/3DDB/RID/\">OSU (MSU/WSU) Range Image Database</a> - Hundreds of real and synthetic images (Formats: gif, homebrew)</li>","updatedAt":"2015-08-05T13:07:49.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"ChristosChristofidis/awesome-deep-learning","categoryHTML":"<h2>Researchers</h2><h3>Datasets</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://sampl.eng.ohio-state.edu\">Signal Analysis and Machine Perception Laboratory</a></li>","updatedAt":"2015-08-05T13:07:49.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"ChristosChristofidis/awesome-deep-learning","categoryHTML":"<h2>Researchers</h2><h3>Datasets</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://www.cs.otago.ac.nz/research/vision/Research/OpticalFlow/opticalflow.html\">Otago Optical Flow Evaluation Sequences</a> - Synthetic and real sequences with machine-readable ground truth optical flow fields, plus tools to generate ground truth for new sequences. (Formats: ppm,tif,homebrew)</li>","updatedAt":"2015-08-05T13:07:49.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"ChristosChristofidis/awesome-deep-learning","categoryHTML":"<h2>Researchers</h2><h3>Datasets</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://www.limsi.fr/\">LIMSI-CNRS</a></li>","updatedAt":"2015-08-05T13:07:49.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"ChristosChristofidis/awesome-deep-learning","categoryHTML":"<h2>Researchers</h2><h3>Datasets</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://www.cee.hw.ac.uk/~mtc/sofa\">SEQUENCES FOR OPTICAL FLOW ANALYSIS (SOFA)</a> - 9 synthetic sequences designed for testing motion analysis applications, including full ground truth of motion and camera parameters. (Formats: gif)</li>","updatedAt":"2015-08-05T13:07:49.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"ChristosChristofidis/awesome-deep-learning","categoryHTML":"<h2>Researchers</h2><h3>Datasets</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://www.cee.hw.ac.uk/~mtc/research.html\">Computer Vision Group</a></li>","updatedAt":"2015-08-05T13:07:49.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"ChristosChristofidis/awesome-deep-learning","categoryHTML":"<h2>Researchers</h2><h3>Datasets</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://www.nada.kth.se/~zucch/CAMERA/PUB/seq.html\">Sequences for Flow Based Reconstruction</a> - synthetic sequence for testing structure from motion algorithms (Formats: pgm)</li>","updatedAt":"2015-08-05T13:07:49.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"ChristosChristofidis/awesome-deep-learning","categoryHTML":"<h2>Researchers</h2><h3>Datasets</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://www-dbv.cs.uni-bonn.de/stereo_data/\">Stereo Images with Ground Truth Disparity and Occlusion</a> - a small set of synthetic images of a hallway with varying amounts of noise added. Use these images to benchmark your stereo algorithm. (Formats: raw, viff (khoros), or tiff)</li>","updatedAt":"2015-08-05T13:07:49.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"ChristosChristofidis/awesome-deep-learning","categoryHTML":"<h2>Researchers</h2><h3>Datasets</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://range.informatik.uni-stuttgart.de\">Stuttgart Range Image Database</a> - A collection of synthetic range images taken from high-resolution polygonal models available on the web (Formats: homebrew)</li>","updatedAt":"2015-08-05T13:07:49.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"ChristosChristofidis/awesome-deep-learning","categoryHTML":"<h2>Researchers</h2><h3>Datasets</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://rvl.www.ecn.purdue.edu/RVL/\">Purdue Robot Vision Lab</a></li>","updatedAt":"2015-08-05T13:07:49.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"ChristosChristofidis/awesome-deep-learning","categoryHTML":"<h2>Researchers</h2><h3>Datasets</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://web.mit.edu/torralba/www/database.html\">The MIT-CSAIL Database of Objects and Scenes</a> - Database for testing multiclass object detection and scene recognition algorithms. Over 72,000 images with 2873 annotated frames. More than 50 annotated object classes. (Formats: jpg)</li>","updatedAt":"2015-08-05T13:07:49.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"ChristosChristofidis/awesome-deep-learning","categoryHTML":"<h2>Researchers</h2><h3>Datasets</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://rvl1.ecn.purdue.edu/RVL/specularity_database/\">The RVL SPEC-DB (SPECularity DataBase)</a> - A collection of over 300 real images of 100 objects taken under three different illuminaiton conditions (Diffuse/Ambient/Directed). -- Use these images to test algorithms for detecting and compensating specular highlights in color images. (Formats: TIFF )</li>","updatedAt":"2015-08-05T13:07:49.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"ChristosChristofidis/awesome-deep-learning","categoryHTML":"<h2>Researchers</h2><h3>Datasets</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://rvl1.ecn.purdue.edu/RVL/\">Robot Vision Laboratory</a></li>","updatedAt":"2015-08-05T13:07:49.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"ChristosChristofidis/awesome-deep-learning","categoryHTML":"<h2>Researchers</h2><h3>Datasets</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://xm2vtsdb.ee.surrey.ac.uk\">The Xm2vts database</a> - The XM2VTSDB contains four digital recordings of 295 people taken over a period of four months. This database contains both image and video data of faces.</li>","updatedAt":"2015-08-05T13:07:49.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"ChristosChristofidis/awesome-deep-learning","categoryHTML":"<h2>Researchers</h2><h3>Datasets</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://i21www.ira.uka.de/image_sequences\">Traffic Image Sequences and 'Marbled Block' Sequence</a> - thousands of frames of digitized traffic image sequences as well as the 'Marbled Block' sequence (grayscale images) (Formats: GIF)</li>","updatedAt":"2015-08-05T13:07:49.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"ChristosChristofidis/awesome-deep-learning","categoryHTML":"<h2>Researchers</h2><h3>Datasets</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"ftp://ftp.iam.unibe.ch/pub/Images/FaceImages\">U Bern Face images</a> - hundreds of images (Formats: Sun rasterfile)</li>","updatedAt":"2015-08-05T13:07:49.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"ChristosChristofidis/awesome-deep-learning","categoryHTML":"<h2>Researchers</h2><h3>Datasets</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"ftp://freebie.engin.umich.edu/pub/misc/textures\">U Michigan textures</a> (Formats: compressed raw)</li>","updatedAt":"2015-08-05T13:07:49.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"ChristosChristofidis/awesome-deep-learning","categoryHTML":"<h2>Researchers</h2><h3>Datasets</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"ftp://sunsite.unc.edu/pub/academic/computer-science/virtual-reality/3d\">UNC's 3D image database</a> - many images (Formats: GIF)</li>","updatedAt":"2015-08-05T13:07:49.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"ChristosChristofidis/awesome-deep-learning","categoryHTML":"<h2>Researchers</h2><h3>Datasets</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://marathon.csee.usf.edu/range/seg-comp/SegComp.html\">USF Range Image Data with Segmentation Ground Truth</a> - 80 image sets (Formats: Sun rasterimage)</li>","updatedAt":"2015-08-05T13:07:49.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"ChristosChristofidis/awesome-deep-learning","categoryHTML":"<h2>Researchers</h2><h3>Datasets</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://www.ee.oulu.fi/research/imag/color/pbfd.html\">University of Oulu Physics-based Face Database</a> - contains color images of faces under different illuminants and camera calibration conditions as well as skin spectral reflectance measurements of each person.</li>","updatedAt":"2015-08-05T13:07:49.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"ChristosChristofidis/awesome-deep-learning","categoryHTML":"<h2>Researchers</h2><h3>Datasets</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://www.ee.oulu.fi/mvmp/\">Machine Vision and Media Processing Unit</a></li>","updatedAt":"2015-08-05T13:07:49.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"ChristosChristofidis/awesome-deep-learning","categoryHTML":"<h2>Researchers</h2><h3>Datasets</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://www.outex.oulu.fi\">University of Oulu Texture Database</a> - Database of 320 surface textures, each captured under three illuminants, six spatial resolutions and nine rotation angles. A set of test suites is also provided so that texture segmentation, classification, and retrieval algorithms can be tested in a standard manner. (Formats: bmp, ras, xv)</li>","updatedAt":"2015-08-05T13:07:49.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"ChristosChristofidis/awesome-deep-learning","categoryHTML":"<h2>Researchers</h2><h3>Datasets</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://www.ee.oulu.fi/mvg\">Machine Vision Group</a></li>","updatedAt":"2015-08-05T13:07:49.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"ChristosChristofidis/awesome-deep-learning","categoryHTML":"<h2>Researchers</h2><h3>Datasets</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"ftp://ftp.uu.net/published/usenix/faces\">Usenix face database</a> - Thousands of face images from many different sites (circa 994)</li>","updatedAt":"2015-08-05T13:07:49.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"ChristosChristofidis/awesome-deep-learning","categoryHTML":"<h2>Researchers</h2><h3>Datasets</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://www-prima.inrialpes.fr/Prima/hall/view_sphere.html\">View Sphere Database</a> - Images of 8 objects seen from many different view points. The view sphere is sampled using a geodesic with 172 images/sphere. Two sets for training and testing are available. (Formats: ppm)</li>","updatedAt":"2015-08-05T13:07:49.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"ChristosChristofidis/awesome-deep-learning","categoryHTML":"<h2>Researchers</h2><h3>Datasets</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://www-prima.inrialpes.fr/Prima/\">PRIMA, GRAVIR</a></li>","updatedAt":"2015-08-05T13:07:49.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"ChristosChristofidis/awesome-deep-learning","categoryHTML":"<h2>Researchers</h2><h3>Datasets</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"ftp://ftp.vislist.com/IMAGERY/\">Vision-list Imagery Archive</a> - Many images, many formats</li>","updatedAt":"2015-08-05T13:07:49.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"ChristosChristofidis/awesome-deep-learning","categoryHTML":"<h2>Researchers</h2><h3>Datasets</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://www.cs.cmu.edu/~owenc/word.htm\">Wiry Object Recognition Database</a> - Thousands of images of a cart, ladder, stool, bicycle, chairs, and cluttered scenes with ground truth labelings of edges and regions. (Formats: jpg)</li>","updatedAt":"2015-08-05T13:07:49.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"ChristosChristofidis/awesome-deep-learning","categoryHTML":"<h2>Researchers</h2><h